name: Red Flame (part 3)
description:
The final piece to a collection.

The female figure is so vast. All women with different body shapes, sizes, and color. I wanted to take skin tone away from these pieces. Give a simple line so the colors really reflect some type of feeling. 

Red and black have been my two favorite combos for awhile. I feel they depict the anger and sadness that comes with life.
 
She's the demon spitter.
